description: DTO class representing a Note in API responses, including fields for id, title, content, creation and update timestamps, along with getters and setters.

classes.name: NoteResponse
classes.description: Data Transfer Object for Notes in API responses, including note identification, content, and timestamps.

methods.description: Returns the unique identifier of the note.

methods.description: Sets the title of the note.

methods.name: getContent
methods.description: Returns the content of the note.

methods.name: setContent
methods.description: Sets the content of the note.
